Package coledev.kyeot.tensorflow.tracking

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MultiBoxTracker
    A tracker wrapping ObjectTracker that also handles non-max suppression and matching existing objects to new detections.
    ObjectTracker
    True object detector/tracker class that tracks objects across consecutive preview frames.
    ObjectTracker.FrameChange
    A class that records a timestamped frame translation delta for optical flow.
    ObjectTracker.Keypoint
    A simple class that records keypoint information, which includes local location, score and type.
    ObjectTracker.PointChange
    A simple class that could calculate Keypoint delta.
